=== TC-VL-001: SQL Injection Verification ===
Date: 2026-05-22
Type: Process validation (meta-skill)

Simulation: Verifying a reported SQLi finding

Phase 1: Pre-conditions
  - Finding: SQLi in /search?q= parameter
  - Source: automated scanner (medium confidence)
  - Target accessible: Yes

Phase 2: Execute & Observe
  - Payload 1: ' OR 1=1-- → HTTP 500 (error-based indicator)
  - Payload 2: ' AND 1=2-- → HTTP 200 (different response = boolean blind)
  - Payload 3: ' UNION SELECT NULL-- → column count mismatch error

Phase 3: Independent Confirmation
  - Method 1: Manual curl with payloads → confirmed
  - Method 2: sqlmap --url="target/search?q=test" → confirmed injectable
  - Two independent methods agree: TRUE POSITIVE

Phase 4: False Positive Elimination
